          <section id="svp">
            <h3>Tool Path Generation for CNC Operations</h3>
            <h5>Guide</h5>
            <p>Mr. Viswesh Srinivasan, SVP Laser Technologies (Dec'13 - Jan'14)</p>
            <h5>Abstract</h5>
            <p>Developed an AutoCAD plugin to nest sheet metal by Common Line nesting and Bump nesting methods. Also created a module in VB.NET to read a CAD drawing and generate the path for a CNC end milling tool. An algorithm to offset a given closed polyline, consisting of straight lines and arcs, by a specified distance, was also devised.
	    </p>
</section>
